EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: A measurement of the binding antidrug antibody in a biological specimen.
A measurement of the neutralizing binding antidrug antibody in a biological specimen.
A measurement of the neutralizing cross-reactive binding antidrug antibody in a biological specimen.

EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCSynonym: H3 Specific IgG Antibody Secreting Cells
